"Recycling cardboard makes sense as it conserves natural resources and is cheaper than incinerating it in the waste-to-energy plant. The collected cardboard is an essential raw material for the production of corrugated cardboard, packaging, and even furniture. Because the technical processing continues to improve, even high-quality cardboard products are made from recycled cardboard." = "回收纸板具有现实意义，既能节约自然资源，又比在垃圾发电厂焚烧更为经济。收集的纸板是生产瓦楞纸板、包装材料乃至家具的重要原料。随着技术工艺的持续改进，如今连高品质纸板制品也能由再生纸板制成。";
