"The Mobile Recycling Center (Mobiler Recyclinghof) brings recycling services directly to your neighborhood. You can drop off bulky waste, electronic devices, metals, and other recyclables. It replaces the former Cargo Tram and E-Tram services, offering a convenient and accessible way to recycle materials that don't belong in regular household waste." = "移动回收中心（Mobiler Recyclinghof）将回收服务直接送到您家附近。您可以在此丢弃大件垃圾、电子设备、金属及其他可回收物。它取代了之前的货运电车和电动电车服务，为回收不属于普通生活垃圾的物品提供了一种便捷易达的方式。";
"The waste must be disposed of in a blue Zuri bag. The blue Zuri bag is available for a fee in retail stores and comes in 10, 17, 35, 60, or 110-liter sizes. Place your Zuri bag container at the designated pickup location before 7 a.m. on the collection day." = "废弃物必须装入蓝色的Zuri垃圾袋处理。蓝色的Zuri垃圾袋可在零售店付费购买，有10升、17升、35升、60升或110升规格可选。请在收集日当天上午7点前，将装有Zuri垃圾袋的容器放置在指定的收集点。";
"The Zurich Waste Disposal and Recycling brings over 30,000 Zuri bags to the Hagenholz waste-to-energy plant every day, where they are environmentally burned. The heat generated from incineration produces ecological power and climate-friendly Zurich heat, which can heat around 170,000 apartments." = "苏黎世废物处理与回收公司（Zürich Entsorgung und Recycling）每日将超过30,000个苏黎世垃圾袋运往哈根霍尔茨垃圾发电厂，并在那里进行环保焚烧。焚烧产生的热量可转化为生态电力和气候友好的苏黎世供暖，为约17万套公寓供暖。";
