"Those who dispose of their household waste in fee-free bags, illegally, or in public trash bins are unfair to those who properly prepare their waste. Illegal dumpers are reported to the police and may face fines of up to several thousand Swiss francs." = "那些将生活垃圾随意丢弃在免费垃圾袋中、非法倾倒或丢入公共垃圾箱的人，对那些规范处理垃圾的人不公平。非法倾倒者将被举报至警方，可能面临高达数千瑞士法郎的罚款。";
